com.mashery.trafficmanager.model.core

Interface Endpoint

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    APIEndpoint, PlanEndpoint

    public interface Endpoint
    API Endpoint being requested. Endpoint belongs to a Service.
    Restriction
    This interface is not intended to be implemented by clients.
    Restriction
    This interface is not intended to be extended by clients.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      API getAPI()
      Returns the API that this Endpoint represents.
      String getExternalID()
      Returns this Endpoint's external identifier.
      Processor getProcessor()
      Returns the Processor configuration for this Endpoint, or null if none.
      HostRequestConfiguration getTargetRequestConfiguration()
      Returns the configuration for target requests.
      boolean isPCIEnabled()
      Returns true if this Endpoint is PCI-enabled.
      boolean isSSLEnabled()
      Returns true if this Endpoint requires that API requests be made over SSL.
